channel.title: How to get silab client working on vista?
channel.description:
im new here so dont laugh at me :D
the owner of this one server told me how to get silab client to work on vista first he told me too.
1.download fire fox at [flash=200,200]http://www.mozila.com/firefox/[/flash]
2. then i right clicked on properties and then clicked compatibility then i made it compatible with windows XP
3. then it worked for like 3 days
4. after that it says error loading silab client
how do i make JAVA trust silabsoft
i went in my fire wall and it says it is trusted but it still wont work
QUESTION: what did i do wrong???
